{
  "id": "adv_event_2208_01_01",
  "title": "先輩と\n遊びたくて",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――夏のとある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Summer",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、1、2！　1、2！\n愛、こころ！　遅れてるわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ 1‚ 2! 1‚ 2!\nAi‚ Kokoro! You're falling behind!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2,
      "endTime": 8.2259182319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい、すみません……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yes‚ sorry…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.432584842,
      "endTime": 12.2449204922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、うっ、うう……\nも、もう、こころは……がくっ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa‚ haa… ugh‚ uuu…\nI-I'm… out of breath…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4449204922,
      "endTime": 22.7870063305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、大丈夫？\nどうしたの？　二人ともなんだかおかしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro‚ are you okay?\nWhat's wrong? Both of you seem strange.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.8666666667,
      "endTime": 29.9725631067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ……もしかして、どこか怪我でもしてるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… Could it be that you got injured somewhere?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1666666667,
      "endTime": 34.4351701419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "だって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6666666667,
      "endTime": 36.6998191038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "昨日ライブ終わったばっかりじゃないですかぁ～\nなのに、どうしてレッスンなんですかぁ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We just finished a live performance yesterday.\nWhy are we having lessons now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0666666667,
      "endTime": 44.5982579508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……どうして葵さんと莉央さんは\nそんなに涼しい顔でレッスンしてられるんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa‚ haa… Why can Aoi-san and Rio-san\nstay so cool while practicing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7666666667,
      "endTime": 53.972345623900004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてって……僕は毎日踊ってるから\n昨日ライブがあってもなくても、関係ないよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why? It's because I dance every day.\nWhether there's a live performance or not‚ it doesn't matter to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.1666666667,
      "endTime": 60.9238778903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "オフも踊るのが当たり前……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's natural to dance even on days off…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1,
      "endTime": 63.7167574406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "ううっ、先輩方はワーカホリックですぅ～\nリズノワはブラック企業ならぬブラックアイドルです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ senpais are workaholics.\nLizNoir is like a black idol company.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.9333333333,
      "endTime": 72.1606611297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、二人とも無駄口叩かない\nまだ始めて二時間よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ stop complaining.\nIt's only been two hours since we started.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3666666667,
      "endTime": 77.3398733192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "オフも私達と一緒にいたいって言い出したのは\n貴方達でしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was you two who said you wanted\nto be with us even on days off‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.5666666667,
      "endTime": 81.8834139441,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こういう意味じゃなかったんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-that's not what I meant…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.1333333333,
      "endTime": 85.9742404302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "もう限界です……。可憐なこころは、莉央さんや\n葵さんみたいな体力おばけにはついていけません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't take it anymore… Delicate Kokoro\ncan't keep up with Rio-san and Aoi-san‚ who are stamina monsters…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.2,
      "endTime": 95.8394435495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "莉央、少し休憩入れようか\n無理をさせて、本当に二人が怪我をしたらいけない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio‚ should we take a little break?\nWe shouldn't push them too hard. We can't afford them getting injured.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.0333333333,
      "endTime": 102.68857320010001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。大切な後輩達だもの\n休みましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right. They're our precious juniors.\nLet's take a break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9,
      "endTime": 107.5090852614,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "た、助かった～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-thank goodness~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.8,
      "endTime": 110.73154196739999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、葵さん……ありがとうございます\nこころは素晴らしい先輩を持って幸せです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ Aoi-san… Thank you so much.\nKokoro is lucky to have wonderful senpais~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.9333333333,
      "endTime": 118.71421136500001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "休憩は十分くらいかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is a ten-minute break enough?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.9,
      "endTime": 121.1811564684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "五分でいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shouldn't we take just 5 minutes?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.4,
      "endTime": 122.7255101919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "鬼です！　こころは今\nリズノワ先輩が鬼アイドルだと確信しました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Evil!\nI'm now convinced that LizNoir senpais are devil idols!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0666666667,
      "endTime": 128.9643506743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あはは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2,
      "endTime": 131.89999999999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "（本当は、オフに先輩方と遊びたかったんだけど……）\n（とてもそんなこと言える空気じゃないなあ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I actually wanted to hang out with senpais on our day off…）\n（But the atmosphere doesn't really allow me to say that…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.0666666667,
      "endTime": 140.8999999999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10366.666666599996
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 142.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "美味しい……レッスンの後は甘いものが\n身に染みるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Delicious… After rehearsals‚\nsweet treats really hit the spot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.2333333333,
      "endTime": 148.2312976784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 148.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "涼しいし、ドリンクバーは飲み放題だし\n夏のファミレスは最強だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's cool here‚ and the drink bar is all-you-can-drink.\nSummer at a family restaurant is the best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.4333333333,
      "endTime": 155.1086194717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 155.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_01_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "僕、夏は踊っている時以外\nここに入り浸っているんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Apart from dancing during summer‚\nI'm always here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.3,
      "endTime": 159.1586195004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 159.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
